data.description: Incredible daylight rambler in Lakeland Village. Rare find with 4-beds/3 full baths. Main floor living w/ Master and 2nd bedroom.  Private deck off of master bedroom also with 5-piece bath en suite.  Huge dining/living rooms with french doors to spacious deck. Kitchen with updated granite counters, eating bar and nook. Fully finished walk out basement with huge rec room, flex space and access to lower deck and terraced back yards.  RV & Boat parking.  Owner's Only access to community lake/beach.
